reviewText: Not too bad but I can't believe she was wearing a jacket in that heat and humidity.

Very annoying hostess, corny humor, and not very informative. Worst of all, she spends about a quarter of the episode raving about the local Westin resort property, showing us the lobby, rooms, suites, spa, pool, etc.  Westin obviously paid for her trip to Malta.
We had been, so it was neat to see some of the sights, but not a lot of details given.
